Introduction
Hello! I'm Sruthilaya S, a dedicated Product Manager with a passion for leveraging technology and innovation to create exceptional digital products that make a difference in users' lives. My journey into product management was fueled by a desire to bridge the gap between technology and user needs, and to shape products that not only solve problems but also delight users. Product management, with its emphasis on customer-centricity, innovation, and cross-functional collaboration, became the perfect avenue for me to realize this aspiration.
Why Product Management?
My pursuit of product management is tueled by a deep-seated belief in the transformative power of exceptional products. I am excited to be part of a dynamic held that challenges me to think creatively, learn continuously, and lead teams in building products that leave a lasting impact on users.
